Weapon Group (Exotic Double Weapons)	CATEGORY:FEAT	TYPE:WeaponGroup.Fighter	VISIBLE:YES		PRETOTALAB:1																	PREVAREQ:UA_VAR_USEWEAPONGROUP,1			DESC:Whenever you take a Weapon Group profi ciency feat, you also gain profi ciency in the exotic double weapons associated with that group. When you take this feat, you gain profi ciency in the exotic double weapons associated with the weapon groups that you already know how to use. Some exotic double weapons require you to be profi cient with two weapon groups to gain profi ciency in their use from this feat.																	SOURCEPAGE:UA	ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Group (Exotic Double Weapons)
Weapon Group (Exotic Weapons)	CATEGORY:FEAT	TYPE:WeaponGroup.Fighter	VISIBLE:YES		PRETOTALAB:1																	PREVAREQ:UA_VAR_USEWEAPONGROUP,1			DESC:When you take this feat, you gain proficiency in the exotic weapons associated with the weapon groups that you already know how to use. Whenever you take a Weapon Group proficiency feat, you also gain proficiency in the exotic weapons (but not the exotic double weapons) associated with that group.																	SOURCEPAGE:UA	ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Group (Exotic Weapons)
