Additional Favored Class	CATEGORY:FEAT	TYPE:General	VISIBLE:YES																			PREVAREQ:UA_VAR_USEADDITIONALFAVOREDCLASSFEAT,1			DESC:Choose a character class, such as ranger. The chosen class is treated as a favored class for the purpose of determining whether your character takes an experience point penalty for Multiclassing. Special: You can gain this feat multiple times. Each time you take the feat, it applies to a new class.	STACK:YES	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:NOCHOICE														SOURCEPAGE:UA	
																																											
